      "writtenOn": "2020-01-10T03:57:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Prefer using expectNoUnmatchedCalls()[1] in your afterEach(), which will make a test fail in the presence of unexpected RPC calls.\n\nOn a similar vein, I recommend using fetchMock.done() to verify that your mock RPCs have been called at least once.\n\n  afterEach(() \u003d\u003e {\n    expect(fetchMock.done()).to.be.true; // All mock RPCs called at least once.\n    expectNoUnmatchedCalls(fetchMock);\n  });\n\n[1] https://cs.corp.google.com/skia/buildbot/golden/modules/test_util.js?l\u003d15",
